headline: Caesars Entertainment (CZR) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of hotel and casino entertainment company Caesars Entertainment (NASDAQ:CZR) jumped 3% in the afternoon session after the broader market rallied on positive economic news that pointed to a resilient U.S. consumer.
